  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/cdf6211390d42bfaa257e83b2d1f2b30.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=117 /></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Magical Bakery is a cooking and management, single-player game, set in an enchanted bakery that sells all sorts of sweets and pastries with a twist — they may contain traces of magic!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/f0cccaaae10fdf03c08827ebd999ef28.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=450 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a life full of magic, challenges, and the joy of creating sweets that will leave a spellbinding impression on your customers. Become the ultimate magical baker and prove yourself worthy to inherit the Magical Bakery! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/7acd429ba2358b3dca6a73eae95755dd.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/8ddcf621b1c8656857ca9480c4ae9d21.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a young magical baker trainee of the Academy of Magical Bakers, it's time to put your magical skills to the test! Create delectable treats and decorate them with magical sprinkles to solve your customers' problems, warm their hearts, or simply make their day brighter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/055523c1d4a168c81a6021bf487d1356.avif?t=1751537106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras_big/055523c1d4a168c81a6021bf487d1356.avif?t=1751537106 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/bcdedf8feef2df0e5ea074bc7138b841.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix, knead, bake, and decorate with flair! Unlock new ingredients and upgrade your bakery with the help of two special NPCs. The merchant and blacksmith are ready to assist you in your quest to make your bakery the go-to spot for magical indulgence!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/3395659fc21f2e4de731bae43ab777c4.avif?t=1751537106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras_big/3395659fc21f2e4de731bae43ab777c4.avif?t=1751537106 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/7a6a0591fe4ba97b081db016e860fd5b.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your destiny awaits! Prove your mastery by passing exams at the Academy of Magical Bakers. Every Sunday, the examiner will visit to check your progress, so rise to the challenge and show your magical skills! Level up to unlock recipes and ingredients, and even harness the power of elementals. Inherit the shop from the old witch owner and bring new life to this magical haven!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/16f6ac590b01b606b081aebd7f883f4b.avif?t=1751537106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras_big/16f6ac590b01b606b081aebd7f883f4b.avif?t=1751537106 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/0f68241f30e7ffac0211638258b988cb.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a cozy management game where you run a magical bakeshop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bake all sorts of sweets and pastries infused with magic to solve your customers' problems and bring them joy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop skills, unlock new ingredients, and upgrade the bakery to your heart's desire</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/78b6d4bbd3c3c58fdbc7d7c72de8ee1b.avif?t=1751537106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras_big/78b6d4bbd3c3c58fdbc7d7c72de8ee1b.avif?t=1751537106 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pass exams at the Academy of Magical Bakers to prove mastery and inherit the shop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an adorable and whimsical visual style that is sure to delight players of all ages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your character  into your ideal magical baker look</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/06e4efcd9b075ac3672222af4c6d43bd.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=468 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/cdf6211390d42bfaa257e83b2d1f2b30.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=117 /></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Magical Bakery is a cooking and management, single-player game, set in an enchanted bakery that sells all sorts of sweets and pastries with a twist — they may contain traces of magic!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/f0cccaaae10fdf03c08827ebd999ef28.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=450 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a life full of magic, challenges, and the joy of creating sweets that will leave a spellbinding impression on your customers. Become the ultimate magical baker and prove yourself worthy to inherit the Magical Bakery! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/7acd429ba2358b3dca6a73eae95755dd.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/8ddcf621b1c8656857ca9480c4ae9d21.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a young magical baker trainee of the Academy of Magical Bakers, it's time to put your magical skills to the test! Create delectable treats and decorate them with magical sprinkles to solve your customers' problems, warm their hearts, or simply make their day brighter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" 