s. Inherit the shop from the old witch owner and bring new life to this magical haven!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/16f6ac590b01b606b081aebd7f883f4b.avif?t=1751537106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras_big/16f6ac590b01b606b081aebd7f883f4b.avif?t=1751537106 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/0f68241f30e7ffac0211638258b988cb.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a cozy management game where you run a magical bakeshop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bake all sorts of sweets and pastries infused with magic to solve your customers' problems and bring them joy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop skills, unlock new ingredients, and upgrade the bakery to your heart's desire</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/78b6d4bbd3c3c58fdbc7d7c72de8ee1b.avif?t=1751537106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras_big/78b6d4bbd3c3c58fdbc7d7c72de8ee1b.avif?t=1751537106 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pass exams at the Academy of Magical Bakers to prove mastery and inherit the shop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an adorable and whimsical visual style that is sure to delight players of all ages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your character  into your ideal magical baker look</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595940/extras/06e4efcd9b075ac3672222af4c6d43bd.avif?t=1751537106\" width=800 height=468 /></span></p>",
